  <brief_title>Prochymal® (Human Adult Stem Cells) Intravenous Infusion Following Acute Myocardial Infarction (AMI)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II, Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of PROCHYMAL® (Ex Vivo Cultured Adult Human Mesenchymal Stem Cells) Intravenous Infusion Following Acute Myocardial Infarction</official_title>
  <sponsors>
